It's one of Disney's famous melodies that's become a chart hit in countries across the world.

But on Thursday afternoon, Karl Stefanovic took on on the challenge to belt out his adaptation of the the classic Frozen tune Let It Go. And his cringeworthy version is sure to send chills down one's spine.

Nine's Today show presenter competed with young Frozen fans, dressed as the animated characters Elsa the Snow Queen and younger sister Anna, as he strains his voice to reach the high notes. 

