The breakfast program was at the Royal Melbourne Show on Thursday afternoon to film segments for its Friday edition.

Co-host Stefanovic gladly accepted the challenge to a Frozen sing-off - complete with hand actions.

However his fellow contestants seem unfazed by the 40-year-old's lack of relative pitch as one girl simply raised her voice to sing over Stefanovic.

While watching the pre-recorded segment, one presenter commented: 'You look like you're in pain there Karl, are you okay?'

To which Stefanovic responded: 'I was just in the moment.'

